description: Creates an Amazon OpenSearch Service-managed VPC endpoint.

parameters.name: DomainArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the domain to create the endpoint for.

parameters.name: VpcOptions
parameters.description: Options to specify the subnets and security groups for the endpoint. SubnetIds (list) --- A list of subnet IDs associated with the VPC endpoints for the domain. If your domain uses multiple Availability Zones, you need to provide two subnet IDs, one per zone. Otherwise, provide only one. (string) --- SecurityGroupIds (list) --- The list of security group IDs associated with the VPC endpoints for the domain. If you do not provide a security group ID, OpenSearch Service uses the default security group for the VPC. (string) ---

nested_params.name: SubnetIds
nested_params.description: A list of subnet IDs associated with the VPC endpoints for the domain. If your domain uses multiple Availability Zones, you need to provide two subnet IDs, one per zone. Otherwise, provide only one.

nested_params.name: SecurityGroupIds
nested_params.description: The list of security group IDs associated with the VPC endpoints for the domain. If you do not provide a security group ID, OpenSearch Service uses the default security group for the VPC.

nested_items.name: VpcEndpoint
nested_items.description: Information about the newly created VPC endpoint.

nested_items.name: VpcEndpointId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the endpoint.

nested_items.name: DomainArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the domain associated with the endpoint.

nested_items.name: VpcOptions
nested_items.description: Options to specify the subnets and security groups for an Amazon OpenSearch Service VPC endpoint.

nested_items.name: VPCId
nested_items.description: The ID for your VPC. Amazon VPC generates this value when you create a VPC.

nested_items.name: SubnetIds
nested_items.description: A list of subnet IDs associated with the VPC endpoints for the domain.

nested_items.name: AvailabilityZones
nested_items.description: The list of Availability Zones associated with the VPC subnets.

nested_items.name: SecurityGroupIds
nested_items.description: The list of security group IDs associated with the VPC endpoints for the domain.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The current status of the endpoint.

nested_items.name: Endpoint
nested_items.description: The connection endpoint ID for connecting to the domain.
